  "monster": {
    "title": "Kawin.",
    "body": "One of the many lords of Pandemonium, Kawin has a skeletal cyan body and a thin, worm-like head.\n\n<lightgrey>Max HP: 183     </lightgrey><lightgrey> Will: +++      </lightgrey><lightgrey>   AC: ++++ ++  </lightgrey><lightgrey>  EV: +         </lightgrey>                \n<lightgrey>    rF: x..     </lightgrey><lightgrey>   rC: +..      </lightgrey><lightgrey>rPois: +        </lightgrey><lightgrey>rNeg: ∞         </lightgrey><darkgrey>rElec: .        </darkgrey>\n<lightgrey>Threat: High    </lightgrey><lightgrey>Class: Demonic  </lightgrey><lightgrey> Size: Large    </lightgrey><lightgrey> Int: Human     </lightgrey>\n\n\nYou have about 93% to hit with the +10 falchion \"Kapodwy\" and 93% to hit with your bite.\nIt has about 61% to hit you.\n\nAttack  Max Damage  After Damaging Hits\nHit     24          Drain speed        \n\nIt is immune to torment; and resistant to miasma.\nIt can see invisible.\nIt can open doors.\nSPELLSET_PLACEHOLDERTo read a description, press the key listed above. (AdB) indicates damage (the sum of A B-sided dice), (x%) indicates the chance to defeat your Will, and (y) indicates the spell range; shown in red if you are in range.\n\nIt is currently targeting the orb of winter.\n\nThis monster has been temporarily summoned to this location. If angered it will immediately vanish, yielding no experience or items; it is incapable of using stairs.",
